Package: gron
Version: 0.7.1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, golang
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/tomnomnom/gron
Description: Make JSON greppable
 gron transforms JSON into discrete assignments, making it easier
 to grep for specific keys and values. It is useful for extracting
 data from complex JSON structures in command-line pipelines.
